    and King's Norton registration districts after 1.10.1912 (forming the following 
    wards of Birmingham County Borough: Acocks Green (until 1.4.1920), Aston, Duddesdon 
    & Nechells, Erdington North, Erdington South, Lozells, St. Bartholomews, Saltley, 
    Small Heath (until 1.4.1920), Sparkbrook (until 1.4.1920), Sparkhill (until 
    1.4.1920), Washwood Heath and Yardley (until 1.4.1920)). See also Table 2, 
    notes (a), (b), (d), (f), (g), (h) and (i).
